<header class="l-section l-section--primary l-section--xl l-section--hero">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="m-hero row justify-content-center">
			<div class="col-md-8">
				<%= image_tag("logo.svg", class: "svg m-hero__logo") %>
				<h4>We are design and development consultants creating digital experiences.</h4>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</header>

<nav class="l-section l-section--dark l-section--xs l-section--navigation js-fixed">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="m-navigation">
			<%= image_tag("logo.svg", class: "svg m-navigation__logo") %>
			<ul class="list-inline">
				<li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#whatwedo">What We Do</a></li>
				<li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#aboutus">About Us</a></li>
				<li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#ourwork">Our Work</a></li>
				<li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#">Contact us</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</nav>

<section class="l-section l-section--white l-section--xxl" id="whatwedo">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row text-center justify-content-center">
			<div class="col-md-8">
				<h2>What We Do</h2>
				<p>We help you build that positive experience right into your product. We provide creative services for multiple facets of the digital industry from mobile applications to web applications.</p>
				<p>Reaching out to your potential customers is harder then it has ever been. We help you plan out your strategy to <span class="italic">attack</span>  from all flanks.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="l-section l-section--info l-section--lg" id="aboutus">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-12">
				<h2 class="text-center">About Us</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- Row 1 -->
		<div class="row align-items-center py-4">
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<h3 class="bold">No More Broken Hearts</h3>
				<p>What sets one designer or developer apart from the rest? We have chosen to deliver amazement, joy and craft, embraced by distinctive creativity.</p>
				<p>You ask for the goods. We deliver the great. We are committed to exceeding your expectations, but not your budget.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<div class="brokenheartBackground m-auto">
					<div class="brokenheartHeart"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- Row 2 -->
		<div class="row align-items-center py-4">
			<div class="col-md-6 order-md-12">
					<h3 class="bold">Creative Machines</h3>
					<p>At VRG, we are less creative machines, and more creative producers of machinations, but in the nicest possible sense.</p>
					<p> We scheme and conspire together, to design and devise intriguing strategies for our clients, and ultimately for their global user base. We <span class="italic">love</span> what we do!</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
				<div class="m-auto creativemachinesBackground">
					<div class="creativemachinesPulley1 animated rotateCW"></div>
					<div class="creativemachinesPulley2 animated rotateCW"></div>
					<div class="bubbles">
						<div class="bubble"></div>
						<div class="bubble"></div>
						<div class="bubble"></div>
						<div class="bubble"></div>
						<div class="bubble"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- Row 3 -->
		<div class="row align-items-center py-4">
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<h3 class="bold">Storytellers</h3>
				<p>Each story becomes a part of history. VRG's creations each tell a story of art borne from need, climaxing with flair and imagining.</p>
				<p>Our client accolades and user experiences spur us on to even greater and higher plains of conceptual form. Let our next story become a part of your history.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<div class="brokenheartBackground m-auto">
					<div class="brokenheartHeart"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
<section class="l-section l-section--white l-section--lg" id="ourwork">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row mb-4">
			<div class="col-md-12">
				<h2 class="text-center">Our Work</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<% @our_work.each do |work| %>
				<div class="col-md-4">
					<div class="m-work">
						<%= image_tag(work["image"], class: "m-work__image img-fluid") %>
						<div class="m-work__caption">
							<h5><%= link_to work["name"], work["url"], target: "_blank" %></h5>
							<p class="text-muted"><%= work["description"] %></p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="l-section l-section--light l-section--sm" id="ourwork">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row align-items-center">
			<% @clients.each do |client| %>
				<div class="col-md-2 col-4">
					<div class="m-client">
						<%= link_to image_tag(client["logo"], class: "img-fluid"), client["url"], target: "_blank" %>
					</div>
				</div>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="l-section l-section--white l-section--sm" id="ourwork">
	<div class="container text-center">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-12">
				<h2 class="text-center">Contact</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-12">
				<p>Got an idea, question or general inquiry? We can help. Drop us a line and we will be happy to chat!</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
